Leaders in missions, missiology, evangelism, and global ministry reveal the titles that shaped their vision and equipped them to better proclaim the gospel.
Faithful Women and Their Extraordinary God by Noël Piper (Crossway)Faithful Women and Their Extraordinary God offers the church two needed narratives.
The women featured in this book were powerfully used by God to spread his gospel and build his church.
Today, I lead Urbana, a conference with the vision of seeing this and every student generation give their whole lives to God’s global mission.
This article is part of CT’s special issue on how women are rethinking global gospel proclamation.